Ms. Tascioni?

17:32.350 --> 17:35.342
Do I? Yes, I do.

17:38.120 --> 17:40.179
BROCHARD:
Do you want to ask it?

17:42.360 --> 17:45.124
(mumbling)

17:45.160 --> 17:46.752
I don't even like penguins.

17:46.790 --> 17:49.793
BROCHARD:
Excuse me?

17:49.830 --> 17:51.491
ELSBETH:
Pengums.

17:51.530 --> 17:53.259
They have nothing
to do with this.

17:53.300 --> 17:56.599
