as it's seven figures.

18:03.850 --> 18:06.501
I'll call you.

18:11.690 --> 18:13.248
Mr. Elfman.

18:13.290 --> 18:14.655
Mrs. Florrick.

18:14.690 --> 18:16.555
Eli talked to you?
He did.

18:16.590 --> 18:18.649
