on a limb for me.

18:23.230 --> 18:25.494
I agree. So ask him
to endorse you later.

18:25.530 --> 18:26.861
I don't like it.

18:26.900 --> 18:28.868
Well, I don't
like asking you.

18:28.900 --> 18:30.765
But, unfortunately,
this is the beginning

18:30.810 --> 18:32.562
of a long line of
distasteful acts.

18:32.610 --> 18:35.238
Every single one of them
a step towards maturity.

18:35.280 --> 18:37.805
Maturity of what?
Of being a good
state's attorney.

18:42.480 --> 18:43.686
Hi.

18:43.720 --> 18:45.449
Hi.

18:45.490 --> 18:46.843
Do you always just wait here?

18:46.890 --> 18:48.858
I just saw
your car pull up.

18:48.890 --> 18:51.552
What's up?
How many hours
do you have left?

18:51.590 --> 18:52.887
Forty-three.

18:52.930 --> 18:55.524
The IP address to the computer

18:55.560 --> 18:57.289
your money was sent to.

18:57.330 --> 18:58.627
A Mr. Kellner.

18:58.670 --> 19:01.332
