phones ringing)

21:27.820 --> 21:29.344
Diane.

21:29.380 --> 21:32.315
Sorry if I don't get up.
Sciatica.

21:32.350 --> 21:34.853
I made a few changes
to the decor.

21:36.820 --> 21:38.629
Your chair squeaked
horribly, by the way.

21:38.660 --> 21:41.049
