knock down a wall or two.

21:41.100 --> 21:44.024
Oh, I still might.
We're having quite a quarter.

21:45.800 --> 21:47.791
About this e-mail...

21:49.670 --> 21:51.535
You opened it?

21:51.570 --> 21:53.800
No, but it is the property
of Lockhart/Gardner,

21:53.840 --> 21:56.479
