B-

23:22.060 --> 23:25.188
4-6-J-Q-

23:25.230 --> 23:27.027
7-9.

23:27.070 --> 23:29.061
David Lee really
gave you back your e-mail?

23:29.100 --> 23:30.761
I was surprised, too.

23:30.810 --> 23:31.606
Here goes.

23:32.570 --> 23:33.901
CAREY:
It's not working.

23:33.940 --> 23:35.430
Hit enter again.

23:36.540 --> 23:39.839
You have a better idea?

23:39.880 --> 23:42.212
Nothing's happening.
