look at the time code.

23:42.250 --> 23:44.445
CAREY: You're kidding-- it's
counting down twice as fast.

23:44.490 --> 23:46.446
DIANE:
Imagine that.

23:48.160 --> 23:49.855
It's not working, Kalinda.

23:49.890 --> 23:50.857
Well, what happened?

23:50.890 --> 23:52.050
