23:52.090 --> 23:53.523
now the _time code
is counting down

23:53.560 --> 23:55.050
twice as fast.

23:55.100 --> 23:56.954
I'm getting on
with the helpline.

23:57.000 --> 23:58.126
No. They'll ask for more money.

23:58.170 --> 23:59.899
You have a lead?

23:59.930 --> 24:01.534
Our money was sent
through a money mule

24:01.570 --> 24:02.662
to somewhere in Russia.

24:02.700 --> 24:03.667
How do you know?

24:03.710 --> 24:04.961
I have a friend who contacted

24:05.010 --> 24:06.136
the Russian service provider.

24:06.170 --> 24:09.037
A friend?
Shh.

24:09.080 --> 24:11.002
(whispers):
Thanks a lot.

24:11.050 --> 24:12.677
How did he do that, your friend?

24:12.710 --> 24:15.019
It's a federal agent.

24:15.050 --> 24:17.177
Trojanlock is working
through a prom,

24:17.220 --> 24:19.609
but we have the money
mule's hard drive,

24:19.650 --> 24:21.618
so we're coordinating
access times.

24:21.660 --> 24:22.957
Good.

24:22.990 --> 24:24.184
Great.

24:24.230 --> 24:26.528
Where are you, Kalinda?

24:27.560 --> 24:28.629
Uh, home.

24:28.660 --> 24:30.628
You want me to come over?

24:30.670 --> 24:32.160
Uh, maybe later.

24:32.200 --> 24:34.191
